description:
This is a 26 minute workout called 'Home Workout for Beginners (2023)' from the channel Hybrid Calisthenics.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Here's an easy way to get started into working out at home! You can start with an exercise you can do and work your way up as you get stronger.
